      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tpm-ass        =    01
                     go to acc-nrm-ass-200
           else if   w-tes-tpm-ass        =    02
                     go to acc-nrm-ass-400
           else if   w-tes-tpm-ass        =    99
                     go to acc-nrm-ass-600
           else      go to acc-nrm-ass-999.
       acc-nrm-ass-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
