      *                  * Se record non New non si ammette la modifi- *
      *                  * ca del valore                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces and
                     v-mod                not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tpm-cpt-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se valore ammesso                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tpm-cpt (1)    not  = 02 and
                     w-rig-tpm-cpt (1)    not  = 03 and
                     w-rig-tpm-cpt (1)    not  = 99
                     go to acc-tpm-cpt-100.
       acc-tpm-cpt-600.
