      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pre-snx-del-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione status di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-pre-snx-del      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test che la distinta non sia presente in altre  *
      *              * distinte come componente                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Routine di controllo                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-tpm-ass        to   w-ctl-dst-dst-tpm      .
           move      w-tes-nrm-ass        to   w-ctl-dst-dst-nrm      .
           perform   ctl-dst-dst-000      thru ctl-dst-dst-999        .
